#Info we want to collect

## Key Dates
* Dates for pre-build (start/finish)
* Event-time (start/finish)
* Dates for strike (start/finish)

## Roles
* Name
* Manager(s)
* Shift length
* Experience required
* Description
* Publish status
* Quantity needed each shift (e.g., "4 people for shift x on day 2")
* Valid when (some roles may be pre-event, during, post event only)

## Publish status
* Draft
* Live
* Retired

## Conscripts
* Name
* Playaname
* Phone number
* Email address
* Skype name
* Arrival date
* Departure date
* Where camping
* Next of Kin
* Gender
* Conditions
* Comfort zones
* Languages spoken
* Link to photo
* Biography
* Feeding requirements (allergies etc)
* Previous burn experience
* Previous experience with each role
* Comments

## Shifts
* Start date
* End date
* Shift length
* Start time
* End time
* Role
* Shift manager
* Shift Logic/Rules
* Quantity needed

## Shift status
* Open
* Pending
* Approved
* Private (e.g. available only to group x, y, z)
* Extended (more people needed)
* Removed from schedule
* At capacity
* Over subscribed

## Groups
* Group name
* Group members

## Shift management
* Turned up
* No show
* Not in a fit state
* Outstanding
